---
// ThankYou — post-submission confirmation with WhatsApp CTA.
// Presentational only; rendered after successful submission.
// Visual: warm sage-wash cream section, human-scene illustration, gold-accented CTA card.
// Copy was lightly tightened for coherence while preserving the approved direction.
---

<section id="funnel-step-thank-you" class="thank-you surface-sage-wash" hidden aria-labelledby="thank-you-heading">
  <div class="thank-you-content">
    <!-- Brand illustration — final thank-you-scene.svg asset. -->
    <div class="thank-you-illustration" aria-hidden="true">
      <img
        src="/images/funnel/thank-you-scene.svg"
        alt=""
        class="thank-you-img"
        width="600"
        height="400"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <h2 id="thank-you-heading" class="thank-you-heading" tabindex="-1">
      ¡Gracias por dar este primer paso!
    </h2>

    <p class="thank-you-body">
      Hoy empezaste a explorar una nueva posibilidad para tu desarrollo
      personal y bienestar integral.
    </p>

    <div class="thank-you-card">
      <h3 class="thank-you-card-heading">
        Agendá tu primer encuentro de orientación sin cargo
      </h3>
      <p class="thank-you-card-text">
        En este encuentro online y personalizado conversaremos sobre lo que hoy
        te importa, responderemos tus dudas y te explicaremos cómo funciona el
        Método VIA®.
      </p>
      <p class="thank-you-card-text">
        Así vas a poder evaluar con claridad si este proceso es el adecuado para
        vos.
      </p>

      <a
        href="https://wa.me/5491126967602"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn thank-you-cta focus-ring-gold"
      >
        Agendar por WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .thank-you {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    padding: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    overflow: clip;
  }

  .thank-you-content {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1080px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ── Illustration ──────────────────────────── */
  .thank-you-illustration {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    justify-self: center;
  }

  .thank-you-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-width: min(100%, 440px);
    max-height: clamp(220px, 38vh, 380px);
    object-fit: contain;
    border-radius: var(--via-scene-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--via-scene-shadow);
  }

  /* ── Typography on cream background ────────── */
  .thank-you-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4.5vw, 2.25rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    outline: none;
    color: var(--via-night-blue);
  }

  .thank-you-body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.58;
    color: var(--via-gray-600);
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  /* ── Card — white panel, gold accent border ── */
  .thank-you-card {
    background: var(--via-white);
    border: 2px solid var(--via-gold);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: clamp(1.4rem, 2.6vw, 1.9rem);
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.08);
  }

  .thank-you-card-heading {
    font-family: var(--ff-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--via-night-blue);
  }

  .thank-you-card-text {
    font-size: 0.925rem;
    line-height: 1.62;
    color: var(--via-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .thank-you-card-text:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ── CTA — night-blue fill, gold hover ──────── */
  .thank-you-cta {
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 0.95rem 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--via-night-blue);
    color: var(--via-white);
    border-color: var(--via-night-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.12);
  }

  .thank-you-cta:hover {
    background: var(--via-gold);
    color: var(--via-night-blue);
    border-color: var(--via-gold);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.22);
  }

  .thank-you-cta:active {
    transform: translateY(1px);
  }

  /* ── Reduced Motion ─────────────────────────── */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .thank-you-cta {
      transition: none !important;
    }

    .thank-you-cta:active {
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  /* ── Mobile ─────────────────────────────────── */

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .thank-you {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem 1.75rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding-top: 2.25rem;
    }

    .thank-you-body {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .thank-you-card {
      padding: 1.35rem;
    }

    .thank-you-card-text {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .thank-you-img {
      max-width: 300px;
      max-height: 230px;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 960px) {
    .thank-you-content {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(280px, 380px);
      column-gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
      text-align: left;
    }

    .thank-you-illustration {
      grid-column: 2;
      grid-row: 1 / span 4;
      justify-self: end;
      align-self: center;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .thank-you-heading,
    .thank-you-body,
    .thank-you-card {
      grid-column: 1;
      justify-self: start;
    }

    .thank-you-body {
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .thank-you-card {
      width: min(100%, 640px);
    }
  }
</style>
